---
import BaseLayout from "src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import CTA from "@components/CTA.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Gutter Cleaning"
  description="Expert gutter cleaning services to protect your home from water damage"
>
  <!-- ============================================ -->
  <!--                    LANDING                   -->
  <!-- ============================================ -->

  <section id="int-hero">
    <h1 id="home-h">Gutter Cleaning</h1>
    <picture>
      <source
        media="(max-width: 600px)"
        srcset="/assets/images/landing-cr-new.jpg"
      />
      <source
        media="(min-width: 601px)"
        srcset="/assets/images/landing-cr-new.jpg"
      />
      <img
        aria-hidden="true"
        decoding="async"
        src="/assets/images/landing-cr-new.jpg"
        alt="drone roof"
        loading="eager"
        width="2500"
        height="1667"
      />
    </picture>
  </section>

  <style>
    @media (max-width: 1023px) {
      #int-hero {
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
  

    <!-- ============================================ -->
<!--             Side By Side Reverse             -->
<!-- ============================================ -->

<section id="sbs-r-870">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <!-- Image Wrapper for Stacking -->
    <div class="cs-images-wrapper">
      <!-- First Image -->
      <picture class="cs-picture">
        <!--Mobile Image-->
        <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset="/assets/images/gutter-cleaning-1.jpg">
        <!--Tablet and above Image-->
        <source media="(min-width: 601px)" srcset="/assets/images/gutter-cleaning-1.jpg">
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          src="/assets/images/gutter-cleaning-1.jpg"
          alt="gutter cleaning"
          width="630"
          height="775"
        >
      </picture>

      <!-- Second Image -->
      <picture class="cs-picture">
        <!--Mobile Image-->
        <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset="/assets/images/gutter-close.jpg">
        <!--Tablet and above Image-->
        <source media="(min-width: 601px)" srcset="/assets/images/gutter-close.jpg">
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          src="/assets/images/gutter-close.jpg"
          alt="golf coaching"
          width="630"
          height="775"
        >
      </picture>

       <!-- Second Image -->
       <picture class="cs-picture">
        <!--Mobile Image-->
        <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset="/assets/images/clean-gutter.jpg">
        <!--Tablet and above Image-->
        <source media="(min-width: 601px)" srcset="/assets/images/clean-gutter.jpg">
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          src="/assets/images/clean-gutter.jpg"
          alt="clean gutter"
          width="630"
          height="775"
        >
      </picture>
    </div>

<!-- Content Section -->
<div class="cs-content">
  <span class="cs-topper">Featured Service</span>
  <h2 class="cs-title">Gutter Cleaning</h2>
  <p class="cs-text">
    Safeguard your home against possible water harm with our expert gutter cleaning solutions. Jammed or blocked troughs can result in grave issues, such as roof leaks, moisture infiltration, and compromised foundations. Our cleaning methods keep your residence dry and secure all year, averting needless fixes and expensive deterioration.
  </p>

  <h3>Why Choose Our Gutter Cleaning Services?</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Trained Specialists:</strong> Our cleaning crew includes certified pros adept at clearing gutters and downspouts. We supply effective, secure, and dependable assistance each time, guaranteeing a debris-free system working as intended.</li>
    <li><strong>Modern Cleaning Gear:</strong> Armed with cutting-edge instruments and tech, we promise a comprehensive clean. From portable implements to robust suction equipment, we ensure every segment of your gutter setup is thoroughly serviced.</li>
    <li><strong>Complete Gutter Attention:</strong> Beyond mere cleaning, we conduct detailed checks to spot possible leaks or defects, offering reassurance and prolonging your gutter’s operational life.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Our Gutter Cleaning Services</h3>
  <h4>Regular Channel Upkeep</h4>
  <p class="cs-text">
    Steady care of your drainage channels thwarts clogs and sustains smooth water passage. Through our scheduled cleaning service, we aid in dodging future hassles and steep repair bills. Our upkeep involves:
    <ul>
      <li>Eliminating leaves, twigs, and other debris that impede proper drainage.</li>
      <li>Unclogging downspouts to maintain free rainwater movement, shielding your home from overflow.</li>
      <li>Verifying proper runoff to prevent possible moisture damage to roofing or footings.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h4>Detailed Channel Inspections</h4>
  <p class="cs-text">
    We go beyond routine cleaning with our in-depth examinations. By reviewing gutters and spouts, we catch early warning signs that may escalate. Our inspection covers:
    <ul>
      <li>Detecting leaks, corrosion, or fissures in the gutter assembly that might trigger water harm.</li>
      <li>Evaluating the positioning and sturdiness of gutters to confirm they operate correctly.</li>
      <li>Suggesting repairs or replacements when essential to head off future complications.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h4>Urgent Channel Clearing</h4>
  <p class="cs-text">
    When storms or downpours clog gutters, immediate action is crucial. Our emergency service aims to:
    <ul>
      <li>Rapidly unclog channels to stave off moisture damage.</li>
      <li>Offer instant fixes to reduce harm from overflowing troughs.</li>
      <li>Confirm proper gutter performance before subsequent weather events.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h4>Protective Gutter Shield Setup</h4>
  <p class="cs-text">
    If continual cleaning is a burden, think about gutter guards. These shields curb debris accumulation, easing upkeep frequency. Our solution features:
    <ul>
      <li>Fitting resilient guards to block leaves and obstructions.</li>
      <li>Guaranteeing water passes unhindered while cutting down on maintenance chores.</li>
      <li>Providing enduring measures that lessen chances of clogs and runovers.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h4>Downspout Purging</h4>
  <p class="cs-text">
    Beyond gutter care, we excel in clearing downspouts. Proper outflow channels are vital for directing rainwater offsite. Our offering comprises:
    <ul>
      <li>Removing obstructions to permit unobstructed runoff and efficient drainage.</li>
      <li>Verifying downspouts are suitably aligned to channel water from your home’s base.</li>
      <li>Inspecting for leaks or breaches in downspouts that might induce moisture damage.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <p class="cs-text">
    Routine gutter upkeep is a key part of maintaining your residence. By choosing our expert cleaning solutions, you defend your investment from moisture issues and keep your gutters operating optimally long-term.
  </p>

  <p class="cs-text">
    Don’t postpone until heavy rains arrive to fix blocked gutters. Reach out now to arrange cleaning and relish the assurance that your home is thoroughly safeguarded against moisture harm.
  </p>
  <a href="/contact" class="cs-button-solid">Book Today</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>



<style>


/*-- -------------------------- -->
<---    Side By Side Reverse    -->
<--- -------------------------- -*/

/* Mobile - 360px */
@media only screen and (min-width: 0rem) {
    #sbs-r-870 {
        padding: var(--sectionPadding);
    }
    #sbs-r-870 .cs-container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 34.375rem; /* 550px */
        margin: auto;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 4rem);
    }
    
    #sbs-r-870 .cs-picture {
  width: 100%; /* Full width of the parent container */
  max-width: 39.375rem; /* Maximum width (e.g., 630px) */
  max-height: 54rem; /* Set height equal to the width to create a square */
  box-shadow: 0px 2.8px 42px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16);
  border-radius: 5%; /* Fully rounded corners, turning it into a circle */
  overflow: hidden;
  align-self: flex-start; /* Ensure the image stays at the top */
  margin-bottom:7rem; /* Add spacing below the image */
}


    #sbs-r-870 .cs-picture img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
    }
    #sbs-r-870 .cs-content {
        text-align: left;
        max-width: 33.875rem; /* 542px */
        box-sizing: border-box;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 1.5rem; /* Add spacing between elements */
        padding: 1.5rem; /* Add padding inside the content area */
    }
    #sbs-r-870 .cs-content h3 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 1rem; /* Space below headings */
    }
    #sbs-r-870 .cs-content h4 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    #sbs-r-870 .cs-content p {
        line-height: 1.8; /* Improve readability */
        margin-bottom: 1rem; /* Space between paragraphs */
    }
    #sbs-r-870 .cs-content ul {
        list-style-type: disc; /* Add bullet points */
        padding-left: 1.5rem; /* Indent list items */
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem; /* Space below the list */
    }
    #sbs-r-870 .cs-content ul li {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem; /* Space between list items */
    }
    #sbs-r-870 .cs-button-solid {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: clamp(2.875rem, 5.5vw, 3.5rem);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 2rem; /* Add spacing above the button */
        color: #fff;
        min-width: 9.375rem;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
        background-color: var(--primary);
        border-radius: 0.25rem;
        display: inline-block;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    #sbs-r-870 .cs-button-solid:before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        height: 100%;
        width: 0%;
        background: #000;
        opacity: 1;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        z-index: -1;
        border-radius: 0.25rem;
        transition: width 0.3s;
    }
    #sbs-r-870 .cs-button-solid:hover:before {
        width: 100%;
    }
}

/* Desktop - 1024px */
@media only screen and (min-width: 64rem) {
    #sbs-r-870 {
        padding: var(--sectionPadding);
    }

    #sbs-r-870 .cs-container {
        flex-direction: row; /* Preserve side-by-side layout for content */
        max-width: 80rem; /* 1280px */
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: flex-start; /* Align everything to the top */
    }

    #sbs-r-870 .cs-images-wrapper {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column; /* Stack images vertically */
        width: 47%; /* Ensure images wrapper occupies the same space as before */
        gap: 5.6rem; /* Maintain spacing between stacked images */
        align-self: flex-start; /* Ensure the images wrapper starts at the top */
    }

    #sbs-r-870 .cs-content {
        width: 53%; /* Retain content width */
        padding: 0;
        order: 1; /* Move content to the right */
    }

    #sbs-r-870 .cs-picture {
        width: 100%; /* Ensure images fill the wrapper */
        height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
    }

    #sbs-r-870 .cs-picture img {
        display: block; /* Prevent inline spacing issues */
        width: 100%; /* Ensure image takes full width of its container */
        height: auto; /* Maintain natural aspect ratio */
        object-fit: cover; /* Ensure content fits within the container */
    }
}



</style>

  <CTA />
</BaseLayout>
